#. Tag: para
#: adm_sudo.xml:569
#, no-c-format
msgid "Running graphical applications with root privileges has security\t implications. It is recommended to enable root access for a graphical\t application only as an exception. It is also recommended to revoke\t the granted root access as soon as the graphical application is closed."
